    <!-- v5.18 -->
    <item>
      <title>Version 5.18</title>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>New</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Group/Ungroup hotkey (Ctrl+Shift+G)</strong> — manually group or ungroup windows of the same app</li>
          <li><strong>Move window hotkey (Opt+Shift+Arrows)</strong> — move window to adjacent slot without swapping</li>
          <li><strong>Drag to move window</strong> — drag window to another slot</li>
          <li>Toggle Group Indicators hotkey (Ctrl+Opt+I) — hide/show group badges</li>
          <li>Group indicator position setting — choose left or right corner</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Improvements</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Smart window distribution</strong> — windows are distributed evenly across slots</li>
          <li><strong>Manual mode improved</strong> — windows of the same app no longer auto-group</li>
          <li>Two Finder/Terminal windows now appear side by side</li>
          <li>Larger snap activation zones at screen edges</li>
          <li>Redesigned custom layout creator</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Fixes</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Fixed Auto-tiling not distributing windows correctly</li>
          <li>Fixed group indicator showing wrong count</li>
          <li>Fixed keyboard swap for same-app windows (e.g., two Cursor windows)</li>
          <li>Fixed drag-and-drop failing with empty window titles</li>
          <li>Fixed inability to drag windows to empty slots</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
